g_format:\"%10s\"}</strong>\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n      </tfoot>\n    </table>\n\n    If you have questions about the status of your registration or purchase please feel free to contact us.\n  </body>\n</html>\n',1,834,1,0,0,NULL),
